weekend_race.race_comments: Kyle Larson has won the NASCAR Cup Series Championship Race at Phoenix Raceway, his 16th career victory in the NASCAR Cup Series. Kyle Larson has won the 2021 NASCAR Cup Series Championship. Prior to the start of the race, the following vehicle(s) dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reason indicated: Nos. 52, 66 (Uapproved adjustments).
